---
import AithaLayout from '../layouts/AithaLayout.astro';
---
<AithaLayout title="Aitha | The Modern Front Desk" description="Aitha captures missed calls, responds by text, gathers the right details, routes urgent issues, and starts the workflows your business depends on.">

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     HERO
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="ap-hero">
  <div class="container ap-hero-inner">
    <div class="ap-hero-text">
      <div class="ap-badge">The Modern Front Desk</div>
      <h1 class="ap-h1">Your Modern<br/>Front Desk,<br/><span class="ap-orange">Always Ready.</span></h1>
      <p class="ap-lead">Aitha captures missed calls, responds by text, gathers the right details, routes urgent issues, and starts the workflows your business depends on — even when no one can pick up.</p>
      <div class="ap-actions">
        <a class="al-btn al-btn-cta al-btn-lg" href="/contact">Get a Free Demo</a>
        <a class="al-btn al-btn-outline al-btn-lg" href="#how-it-works">See How It Works</a>
      </div>
      <p class="ap-tagline">Built for small businesses · No call left unanswered · Customized to your workflow</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ap-phone-stack">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="ap-phone-card">
        <div class="ap-card-label">Incoming call</div>
        <p class="ap-card-title">Missed call from a customer</p>
        <p class="ap-card-sub">Your staff is busy — but the customer still needs help.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 2: Aitha conversation -->
      <div class="ap-phone-card ap-phone-featured">
        <div class="ap-card-label">Aitha responding</div>
        <div class="ap-bubble ap-bubble-aitha">Hi — sorry we missed your call. How can we help?</div>
        <div class="ap-bubble ap-bubble-in">I have a leak and need someone out today.</div>
        <div class="ap-bubble ap-bubble-out">Got it. Is water actively running or causing damage right now?</div>
        <div class="ap-bubble ap-bubble-in">No damage yet, but it's getting worse.</div>
        <div class="ap-bubble ap-bubble-out">I'll flag this as urgent and have someone call you within the hour.</div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="ap-phone-card">
        <div class="ap-card-label">Workflow started</div>
        <p class="ap-card-title">Routed to the right person</p>
        <p class="ap-card-sub">Urgency, details, and contact info are organized for your team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats bar -->
  <div class="ap-stats-bar">
    <div class="container ap-stats-inner">
      <div class="ap-stat"><strong>30%</strong><span>of calls can go unanswered</span></div>
      <div class="ap-stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="ap-stat"><strong>&lt; 60 s</strong><span>customers expect a fast reply</span></div>
      <div class="ap-stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="ap-stat"><strong>24/7</strong><span>after-hours call capture</span></div>
      <div class="ap-stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="ap-stat"><strong>100%</strong><span>of conversations logged</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     PROBLEM
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="ap-section ap-section-light" id="problem">
  <div class="container ap-two-col">
    <div>
      <div class="ap-eyebrow">The Problem</div>
      <h2 class="ap-h2">Your customers do not care that your office is busy.</h2>
      <p class="ap-body">They expect a fast response. Every missed call is a potential lost job, a frustrated tenant, or a customer who moved on to a competitor. Aitha gives your business a clean, professional front-desk layer — available around the clock.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ap-card ap-problem-card">
      <ul class="ap-list">
        <li>Missed calls silently become lost opportunities.</li>
        <li>After-hours messages get buried until the next morning.</li>
        <li>Urgent issues interrupt the wrong people at the wrong time.</li>
        <li>Routine requests still need a record but nobody writes one down.</li>
        <li>Staff capacity runs out before customer demand does.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     FEATURES
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="ap-section" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ap-section-header">
      <div class="ap-eyebrow">What Aitha Does</div>
      <h2 class="ap-h2">From customer message to organized action.</h2>
      <p class="ap-body ap-section-sub">Aitha handles the gap between missed and handled, so your team sees organized, actionable requests instead of a pile of messages to sort through.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ap-feature-grid">
      <div class="ap-card ap-feature-card">
        <div class="ap-feature-icon ap-icon-teal">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 9.81 19.79 19.79 0 01.02 1.18 2 2 0 012 0h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 7.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 14.92z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Missed call response</h3>
        <p>Aitha texts a caller back after a missed call and asks what they need — before they call a competitor.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-card ap-feature-card">
        <div class="ap-feature-icon ap-icon-teal">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Conversational text intake</h3>
        <p>Aitha collects the right information through a natural back-and-forth conversation, organized for your team.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-card ap-feature-card">
        <div class="ap-feature-icon ap-icon-orange">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Urgency triage</h3>
        <p>Aitha separates true emergencies from routine requests so urgent issues reach the right person fast.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-card ap-feature-card">
        <div class="ap-feature-icon ap-icon-teal">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/><path d="M13 6h3a2 2 0 012 2v7M11 18H8a2 2 0 01-2-2V9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Smart routing</h3>
        <p>Notify a manager, technician, vendor, or staff member based on your custom routing rules.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-card ap-feature-card">
        <div class="ap-feature-icon ap-icon-teal">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Automatic records</h3>
        <p>Every interaction creates a log so nothing gets forgotten, lost, or scattered across personal inboxes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-card ap-feature-card">
        <div class="ap-feature-icon ap-icon-orange">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Workflow triggers</h3>
        <p>Kick off forms, tasks, scheduling, CRM updates, and automations the moment a message comes in.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     HOW IT WORKS (dark)
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="ap-section ap-section-dark" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ap-section-header">
      <div class="ap-eyebrow ap-eyebrow-teal">How It Works</div>
      <h2 class="ap-h2 ap-h2-white">Aitha fills the gap between missed and handled.</h2>
      <p class="ap-body ap-body-muted">Three steps, zero dropped balls.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ap-steps">
      <div class="ap-step">
        <div class="ap-step-num">01</div>
        <div class="ap-step-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 9.81 19.79 19.79 0 01.02 1.18 2 2 0 012 0h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 7.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 14.92z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Customer reaches out</h3>
        <p>They call, text, or submit a request — Aitha is always listening, day or night.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-step-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="ap-step">
        <div class="ap-step-num">02</div>
        <div class="ap-step-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Aitha asks smart questions</h3>
        <p>A natural conversation collects the details your team needs and checks urgency — automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-step-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="ap-step">
        <div class="ap-step-num">03</div>
        <div class="ap-step-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FF7A30" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"/><polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>The workflow moves</h3>
        <p>Your team gets a record, an alert, a task, or the next step — already organized and ready to act on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     INDUSTRIES / USE CASES
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="ap-section ap-section-light" id="industries">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ap-section-header">
      <div class="ap-eyebrow">Industries</div>
      <h2 class="ap-h2">Built for the work that normally lives in someone's head.</h2>
      <p class="ap-body ap-section-sub">Aitha fits wherever calls and messages slip through the cracks — without requiring a full-time admin hire.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ap-industry-grid">
      <div class="ap-card ap-industry-card">
        <div class="ap-industry-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Property Management</h3>
        <p>Tenant maintenance requests, vendor routing, urgency triage, and automatic records — without constant phone interruptions.</p>
        <ul class="ap-mini-list">
          <li>After-hours emergency triage</li>
          <li>Vendor dispatch workflows</li>
          <li>Maintenance request logs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-card ap-industry-card">
        <div class="ap-industry-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Service Businesses</h3>
        <p>Plumbers, electricians, HVAC, cleaners — Aitha captures missed calls, qualifies the job, and starts the booking workflow.</p>
        <ul class="ap-mini-list">
          <li>Missed call recovery via SMS</li>
          <li>Job qualification questions</li>
          <li>Scheduling workflow triggers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-card ap-industry-card">
        <div class="ap-industry-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v16"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Local Offices</h3>
        <p>Busy phone lines, repetitive intake questions, after-hours messages — Aitha handles it all so staff can stay focused.</p>
        <ul class="ap-mini-list">
          <li>After-hours message capture</li>
          <li>Callback request queue</li>
          <li>Intake form automation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SOCIAL PROOF / TRUST STRIP
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="ap-trust-section">
  <div class="container ap-trust-inner">
    <div class="ap-trust-text">
      <div class="ap-eyebrow ap-eyebrow-teal">Why It Matters</div>
      <h2 class="ap-h2 ap-h2-white">Every missed call is a decision point.</h2>
      <p class="ap-body ap-body-muted">Customers who do not get a fast response often move on without saying anything. Aitha makes sure the first contact is always handled professionally — even at 11 PM on a Saturday.</p>
      <a class="al-btn al-btn-teal al-btn-lg" href="/contact" style="margin-top:32px;">Start Recovering Missed Revenue</a>
    </div>
    <div class="ap-trust-cards">
      <div class="ap-trust-card">
        <div class="ap-trust-num">30%</div>
        <p>of business calls can go unanswered during peak hours</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-trust-card">
        <div class="ap-trust-num">78%</div>
        <p>of customers buy from the first business that responds</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-trust-card">
        <div class="ap-trust-num">24/7</div>
        <p>Aitha works around the clock so your team does not have to</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ap-trust-card">
        <div class="ap-trust-num">100%</div>
        <p>of conversations logged with organized records for your team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     FINAL CTA
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="ap-section ap-cta-section">
  <div class="container ap-cta-inner">
    <div class="ap-eyebrow">Get Started</div>
    <h2 class="ap-h2">Let Aitha catch the next missed call before it becomes missed revenue.</h2>
    <p class="ap-body" style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 36px;">Start with a free TaskRocket workflow review. We will map exactly where Aitha fits into your business and show you what it looks like in practice.</p>
    <div class="ap-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
      <a class="al-btn al-btn-cta al-btn-lg" href="/contact">Get a Free Workflow Review</a>
      <a class="al-btn al-btn-outline al-btn-lg" href="/">Learn About TaskRocket</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</AithaLayout>

<style>
/* ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   Aitha Page Styles
   All selectors prefixed with .ap- to avoid any collision with
   global TaskRocket styles.
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

/* ── Shared tokens ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
.ap-section        { padding: 100px 0; }
.ap-section-light  { background: #F8FAFC; }
.ap-section-dark   { background: #101828; }

.ap-eyebrow {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 0.76rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: 0.13em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #FF7A30;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.ap-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 22px; height: 2px; background: currentColor; }
.ap-eyebrow-teal { color: #2DD4BF; }

.ap-h2 {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  line-height: 1.07;
  margin: 0 0 18px;
  color: #101828;
}
.ap-h2-white { color: white; }
.ap-body { font-size: 1.08rem; color: #475467; max-width: 640px; }
.ap-body-muted { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }
.ap-orange { color: #FF7A30; }

.ap-card {
  background: white;
  border: 1.5px solid #E4EAF0;
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 32px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(16,24,40,0.06);
}

.ap-section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}
.ap-section-header .ap-eyebrow { display: flex; justify-content: center; }
.ap-section-header .ap-body { margin: 0 auto; }
.ap-section-sub { text-align: center; }

/* ── Hero ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.ap-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #101828 0%, #1A2A3A 100%);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.ap-hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -20%;
  right: -10%;
  width: 700px;
  height: 700px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(45,212,191,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.ap-hero::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -10%;
  left: -5%;
  width: 500px;
  height: 500px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,122,48,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.ap-hero-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 120px 0 0;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.ap-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(45,212,191,0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(45,212,191,0.3);
  color: #2DD4BF;
  font-size: 0.76rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 6px 16px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.ap-h1 {
  font-size: clamp(42px, 5.5vw, 76px);
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.065em;
  line-height: 1.02;
  color: white;
  margin: 0 0 24px;
}
.ap-lead {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
  max-width: 540px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}
.ap-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 36px;
}
.ap-tagline {
  margin-top: 22px;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
}

/* Phone stack */
.ap-phone-stack {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
}
.ap-phone-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 20px 24px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
}
.ap-phone-featured {
  border-color: rgba(45,212,191,0.4);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(45,212,191,0.1);
}
.ap-card-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.ap-card-title { color: white; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0 0 4px; }
.ap-card-sub   { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 0.86rem; margin: 0; }
.ap-bubble {
  display: block;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  line-height: 1.5;
  max-width: 90%;
  margin: 6px 0;
}
.ap-bubble-aitha {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D9488, #2DD4BF);
  color: white;
}
.ap-bubble-in {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
}
.ap-bubble-out {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  color: #101828;
  margin-left: auto;
}

/* Stats bar */
.ap-stats-bar {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  margin-top: 60px;
  padding: 24px 0;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.ap-stats-inner {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.ap-stat {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 12px 36px;
}
.ap-stat strong {
  font-size: 1.7rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: white;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
}
.ap-stat span {
  font-size: 0.76rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.42);
  margin-top: 2px;
  text-align: center;
}
.ap-stat-divider {
  width: 1px;
  height: 40px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}

/* ── Problem ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.ap-two-col {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 70px;
  align-items: center;
}
.ap-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
}
